<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 06:20:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>印尼顾问称普拉博沃将于下月访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesias-prabowo-visit-china-next-month-says-adviser-2024-10-07/</link><description>印度尼西亚当选总统普拉博沃·苏比安托 (Prabowo Subianto) 的高级顾问周一表示，他将于下个月访问中国，会见投资者，并邀请他们参与一个巨型海堤项目。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 05:08:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesias-prabowo-visit-china-next-month-says-adviser-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>马尔代夫总统穆伊祖将在经济困境中会见印度莫迪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/maldives-president-muizzu-meet-indias-modi-amid-economic-woes-2024-10-07/</link><description>马尔代夫总统穆罕默德·穆伊祖将于周一在为期五天的国事访问期间与印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪举行会谈，希望在马尔代夫这个印度洋国家从经济危机中复苏之际，得到新德里的持续支持。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 04:46:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/maldives-president-muizzu-meet-indias-modi-amid-economic-woes-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>9月份中国黄金储备连续第五个月保持不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-gold-reserves-unchanged-fifth-straight-month-september-2024-10-07/</link><description>周一官方数据显示，中国央行9月份连续第五个月停止购买黄金作为储备，主要是由于黄金价格飙升。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 02:35:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-gold-reserves-unchanged-fifth-straight-month-september-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>日本引领亚洲股市上涨，美国就业人数井喷后美元坚挺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-07/</link><description>亚洲股市上涨，美元兑日元汇率周一创下七周新高，此前美国劳动力市场数据井喷，消除了人们对经济衰退的担忧，并刺激降息押注大幅削减。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 00:50:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，台湾前总统蔡英文将进行敏感的布拉格访问</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/former-taiwan-president-tsai-make-sensitive-prague-visit-sources-say-2024-10-07/</link><description>三名知情人士告诉路透社，台湾前总统蔡英文将于本月访问捷克共和国，对于北京多次谴责为“分裂分子”的一位高级政治家来说，这是一次敏感的访问。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 00:35:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/former-taiwan-president-tsai-make-sensitive-prague-visit-sources-say-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>三星第三季度利润复苏势头减弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/samsungs-profit-recovery-seen-weakening-q3-2024-10-06/</link><description>该公司在人工智能热潮中获利的速度缓慢。</description><pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 23:37:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/samsungs-profit-recovery-seen-weakening-q3-2024-10-06/</guid></item><item><title>大使馆称卡拉奇机场附近发生“恐怖袭击”，造成两名中国公民死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/least-one-dead-10-injured-explosion-near-karachi-airport-geo-news-says-2024-10-06/</link><description>中国驻巴基斯坦大使馆表示，周日晚间，巴基斯坦南部城市卡拉奇国际机场附近发生爆炸，造成两名中国公民死亡，称这是一起“恐怖袭击”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 19:58:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/least-one-dead-10-injured-explosion-near-karachi-airport-geo-news-says-2024-10-06/</guid></item><item><title>据《华尔街日报》报道，中国黑客攻破了美国法院窃听系统</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/chinese-hackers-breached-us-court-wiretap-systems-wsj-reports-2024-10-06/</link><description>据《华尔街日报》周六报道，中国黑客访问了美国宽带提供商的网络，并从联邦政府用于法院授权窃听的系统中获取了信息。</description><pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 06:45:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/chinese-hackers-breached-us-court-wiretap-systems-wsj-reports-2024-10-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国与朝鲜签署合作誓言庆祝建交75周年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-north-korea-mark-75th-anniversary-ties-with-vows-cooperation-2024-10-05/</link><description>据平壤官方通讯社朝中社报道，中国和朝鲜领导人周日誓言要在两国建交 75 周年之际加强双边合作。</description><pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 22:58:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-north-korea-mark-75th-anniversary-ties-with-vows-cooperation-2024-10-05/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车首席执行官：应允许中国汽车制造商通过在欧盟投资以避免关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-ceo-chinese-automakers-should-be-allowed-avert-tariffs-by-investing-eu-2024-10-05/</link><description>即使德国及其汽车制造商拒绝了，欧盟仍将继续对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税。</description><pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 22:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-ceo-chinese-automakers-should-be-allowed-avert-tariffs-by-investing-eu-2024-10-05/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统称中华人民共和国“不可能”成为我们的祖国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/impossible-peoples-republic-china-be-our-motherland-taiwan-president-says-2024-10-05/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德周六表示，中华人民共和国“不可能”成为台湾的祖国，因为台湾有更古老的政治根源。</description><pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 13:41:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/impossible-peoples-republic-china-be-our-motherland-taiwan-president-says-2024-10-05/</guid></item><item><title>新华社报道，欧盟计划对中国电动汽车征收关税，不利于两国关系和绿色雄心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-plan-press-ahead-with-china-ev-tariffs-bad-ties-green-ambitions-xinhua-2024-10-05/</link><description>新华社周六表示，欧盟委员会决定对中国制造的电动汽车加征关税，可能会破坏中国与欧盟数十年的合作，并危及气候变化目标。</description><pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 09:12:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-plan-press-ahead-with-china-ev-tariffs-bad-ties-green-ambitions-xinhua-2024-10-05/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称，刺激措施后中国房屋销售量上升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-home-sales-rise-after-stimulus-measures-state-media-says-2024-10-05/</link><description>官方媒体周六表示，自9月底以来，一系列房地产刺激措施提振了中国陷入困境的房地产市场，国庆假期期间中国房屋销售量出现增长。</description><pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 05:57:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-home-sales-rise-after-stimulus-measures-state-media-says-2024-10-05/</guid></item><item><title>外交部称已有200多名中国公民撤离黎巴嫩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/more-than-200-chinese-citizens-evacuated-lebanon-foreign-ministry-says-2024-10-05/</link><description>中国外交部周六表示，已有200多名中国公民安全撤离黎巴嫩。</description><pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 05:33:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/more-than-200-chinese-citizens-evacuated-lebanon-foreign-ministry-says-2024-10-05/</guid></item><item><title>两名英国男子否认为中国从事间谍活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/two-british-men-deny-spying-china-2024-10-04/</link><description>周五，两名英国人对为中国从事间谍活动的指控表示无罪，其中包括一名英国高级议员的前研究员。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 13:58:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/two-british-men-deny-spying-china-2024-10-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>